title: THE DAY HAS COME! Lunchbox Tests Out If He’s The Top 25 Most Famous People in Nashville + Aaron Goodvin Blows Us Away with “Lonely Drum” Performance + Bobby’s Update on Colonoscopy
itunes:title: THE DAY HAS COME! Lunchbox Tests Out If He’s The Top 25 Most Famous People in Nashville + Aaron Goodvin Blows Us Away with “Lonely Drum” Performance + Bobby’s Update on Colonoscopy
description:
Lunchbox went out to the tour bus to see if anyone would recognize him or yell for him... is he the top 25 most famous people in Nashville? Aaron Goodvin stops by to play his song “Lonely Drum” which Bobby featured on the Dance Party after his very creative pitch. Bobby gives an update on when he is getting his colonoscopy.
